<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.9">
<l>āvā rārtuṇaiyeṉṟalainīrkkaṭa luḷaḻuntu</l>
<l>nāvāy pōlpiṟavik kaṭaluṇiṉṟu nāṉtuḷaṅkat</l>
<l>tēvār kōlattoṭun tiruccakkarañ caṅkiṉoṭu</l>
<l>māvā veṉṟaruḷ ceytaṭiyēṉoṭu māṉāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When, like a ship sinking in the ocean with agitated water, saying</l>
<l>“who will be there as help?”, I swayed in the ocean of birth,</l>
<l>with the full beauty of a deity and with luminous discus and conch</l>
<l>he did [me] the grace of calling “hey, hey” [and] become one with me, [his] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
